<plot>A documentary on French film composer 'Georges Delerue' (qv) who composed scores for 'Ken Russell' (qv) films _French Dressing (1963)_ (qv) and _Women In Love (1970)_ (qv) as well as films for 'Alain Resnais' (qv) and other French directors. The film title is a play on Shoot the Pianist a film he scored in 1960.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?155723</url></doc>
